<br>
also..lots of knowledgeable people have better answers then i can come up with. <br>
<br>
if you need any info on what to look forward to when u hit lvl 200..ask away. <br>
<br>
in the mean time i can post some info i have found semi usefull.<br>
<br>
bows: i have tried a ql 178 pow in pvp...not the best idea in the world. even with a 14% scope...the equip time is WAY to long and the clip size is way to small. <br>
<br>
reet tech jr is still the best way to go. i also get higher crits with my reet vs my pow. <br>
<br>
at lvl 200..with 2 bow clusters i only have 907 bow. i have to run bow expertise just to equip a ql 200 bow.<br>
<br>
god we need a bow buff. <br>
<br>
i tried servants armor for a while..went back to my MK2 armor from the den. its very very worth camping for this armor. the amount of HP and ncu it ads deffinately outways the small bonuses that servents gets u. i have 7200 HP with ql 200 imps, red suit, 2 eggs and full MK2 armor (cept one sleave which i lost somehow). once u get to the 180+ area..its really all about HP cuz you will do lots of pvp more then likely. <br>
<br>
my pvp buffs i have (i dont fight/duel clanners so im always outside buffd): obviousely all our own buffs-chem/fire fists, lesser rage, brawl exp, ma exp, df, velocity, uvc, first strike (i need this cuz with a 14% scope my phys init is like 190 lol), bow expertise, si/pm exp for uvc/kali, kali. <br>
<br>
my outside buffs i will always have before i pvp: essence, run buff from a fixer (1750ish run speed with that and 1k board and velocity), rrfe from a soldier. Now..if i have the room i try to get a doc HP buff gettin me in the 9k hp range, and HE from an NT. a good fixer hot is nice if i have the ncu buff also. <br>
<br>
i almost alway go all bow in 2ho/mmd at first. in big battles..we are cannon fodder if u run up into the crowd. i tend to stay back some and use my aimed/fling for a while till i see a good opportunity to run in and finish them off. <br>
<br>
this actually works very well on gettin kills..cuz if u get off a good alpha...and someone else finishes that toon of..u can still get credit. the pow bow is actually good in big battles like that where u r stayin on the edges..good range and fast aimed recycle. <br>
<br>
i dont know wtf im gonna do with the lls/uvc/mop/bow nerfs next patch..if it happens. personally i think we may be DOOMED as pvpers anymore cept in duels..and duels are for farmers as far as im concerned.<br>
<br>
only time i will duel a clanner is if he is out of my title range. im a novice so will only duel clanners who are rookie and under. just for fun. not cuz i mind losing my title..but because i want every point from omni..so no farming at all. <br>
<br>
if you need any ideas or advice..feel free to msg me ingame. i can post up my equipment, give advice on IP allocation, show u my implants etc. <br>
<br>
celestiness 200 novice clan MA, advisor to Apocalype<br>
